fields.name: On mastodon to learn about politics and people. “Life’s river shall rise, that only the strong shall survive.”
fields.value: Also enjoy all things related to art and nature.

fields.name: Now that I’ve been on this site for a bit, I’m realizing maybe I don’t want to read so much about politics anymore..too toxic in US. I’m leaning more towards art, and positivity and likeminded people. Seems real friendly here!
